Description: "
Update a monitor. Pass any subset of fields to patch: `name`, `status` ("active" | "paused"), `schedule`, `targets`, `goal`, `judgeEnabled`, `webhook`, `notification`, `retentionDays`.

**Usage Example:**
```json
{
  "name": "firecrawl_monitor_update",
  "arguments": {
    "id": "mon_abc123",
    "body": { "status": "paused" }
  }
}
```
